#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/01_The_Elves_Besieged.cfg:235
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Sixteen years into her rule, Asheviere turned her attention to the wood "
"elves living in the great forest southwest of Wesnoth, whom she despised. "
"Orcish mercenaries were hired and dispatched to bring about their ruin."
msgstr ""
"Δεκαέξι χρόνια  στην εξουσία, η Άσεβιρ έριξε την προσοχή της στα Ξωτικά του "
"Δάσους που ζούσαν στο μεγάλο δάσος νοτιοδυτικά του Γουέσνοθ, που "
"περιφρονούσε. Μισθοφόροι ορκ πληρώθηκαν και στάλθηκαν να τα αφανίσουν."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/01_The_Elves_Besieged.cfg:239
msgid ""
"Master Delfador! Look, there are orcs coming from all directions! What shall "
"we do?"
msgstr "Αφέντη Ντεφάλντορ! Κοίτα, Ορκ πλησιάζουν από παντού! Τι θα κάνουμε;"

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/01_The_Elves_Besieged.cfg:243
msgid "There are too many to fight, far too many. We must escape!"
msgstr ""
"Είναι πολλοί για να τους πολεμήσουμε, πάρα πολλοί. Πρέπει να διαφύγουμε! "

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/01_The_Elves_Besieged.cfg:247
msgid "But to where? This is the only home we have! What about the elves?"
msgstr "Που όμως; Αυτό είναι το μόνο σπίτι που έχουμε! Τι θα γίνουν τα Ξωτικά;"

#. [message]: speaker=Galdrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/01_The_Elves_Besieged.cfg:251
msgid ""
"We will fight them, but you must escape, Konrad. It is imperative that you "
"escape!"
msgstr ""
"Θα τους πολεμήσουμε εμείς, αλλά εσύ πρέπει να φύγεις, Κώνραντ. Είναι "
"σημαντικό να φύγεις!"

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/01_The_Elves_Besieged.cfg:255
msgid ""
"We will go north. Perhaps we can reach the Isle of Alduin. If we can make it "
"there, surely we will be safe. Konrad, we must recruit some elves to help "
"us, and then you must make it to the sign post in the north-west. I will "
"protect you!"
msgstr ""
"Θα πάμε βόρεια. Ίσως καταφέρουμε να φτάσουμε το Νησί του Άντουιν. Άμα τα "
"επιζήσουμε μέχρι εκεί, σίγουρα θα είμαστε ασφαλείς. Κώνραντ, πρέπει να "
"στρατολογήσουμε μερικά Ξωτικά για να μας βοηθήσουν, και τότε πρέπει να "
"φτάσουμε στο σημάδι βορειοδυτικά. Θα σε προστατέψω!"

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/01_The_Elves_Besieged.cfg:259
msgid "Very well, let us hurry!"
msgstr "Πολύ καλά, ας βιαστούμε!"

#. [message]: speaker=Urug-Telfar
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/01_The_Elves_Besieged.cfg:264
msgid ""
"Attack the elves, my grunts, and take their villages. Let us claim this land "
"for the Queen!"
msgstr ""
"Επιτεθείτε στα ξωτικά, λύκοι μου, και πάρτε τα χωριά τους. Ας διεκδικήσουμε "
"αυτή τη γη για την Βασίλισσα!"

#. [message]: speaker=Knafa-Tan
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/01_The_Elves_Besieged.cfg:272
msgid ""
"Remember, it is rumored that the filthy mage and one that he protects are in "
"these parts. They are the ones we want!"
msgstr ""
"Θημίσου, υπάρχει μία φήμη ότι ένα βρωμερός μάγος που προστατεύει έναν μικρό "
"υπάρχει σε αυτά τα μέρη. Αυτούς θέλουμαι!"

#. [message]: speaker=Knafa-Tan
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/01_The_Elves_Besieged.cfg:278
msgid "Ha ha! We will rip the filthy elves to pieces!"
msgstr "Χα χα! Θα κόψουμε τα βρώμικα ξωτικά σε κομματάκια!"

#. [message]: speaker=Galdrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/01_The_Elves_Besieged.cfg:283
msgid "Let them come. We will fight them with all we have!"
msgstr "Ας έρθουν. Θα τους πολεμήσουμε με ότι έχουμε!"

#. [message]: speaker=Chantal
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/01_The_Elves_Besieged.cfg:287
msgid "Be careful, Konrad! Guard him well, Delfador!"
msgstr "Πρόσεχε, Κώνραντ! Φύλαξέ τον καλά, Ντεφάλντορ!"

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/01_The_Elves_Besieged.cfg:291
msgid "And so it has begun!"
msgstr "Έτσι, αρχίζει."

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/01_The_Elves_Besieged.cfg:310
msgid "OK, we have made it this far! But where do we go next?"
msgstr "Εντάξει, φτάσαμε μέχρι εδώ! Που πάμε τώρα;"

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/01_The_Elves_Besieged.cfg:314
msgid ""
"We must travel north, and try to make it to the Isle of Alduin. Hopefully we "
"will find refuge there."
msgstr ""
"Θα ταξιδέψουμε βόρια, για το Νησί του Άνντουιν. Ελπίζω να βρούμε καταφύγιο "
"εκεί."

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/01_The_Elves_Besieged.cfg:318
msgid ""
"Of course you are right, Delfador. But what will become of the elves here?"
msgstr "Φυσικά, Ντεφάλντορ. Αλλά τι θα απογίνουν τα ξωτικά εδώ;"

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/01_The_Elves_Besieged.cfg:322
msgid ""
"The elves will fight. They may even prevail. But I fear things do not bode "
"well for them. Let us not speak of it now. Onward!"
msgstr ""
"Τα ξωτικά θα πολεμήσουν. Μπορεί και να επικρατήσουν. Αλλά φοβάμαι ότι τα "
"πράγματα δεν θα πάνε καλά γι'αυτούς. Μήν αργούμε άλλο. Πάμε!"

#. [message]: speaker=Chantal
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/01_The_Elves_Besieged.cfg:326
msgid "Good luck, Konrad! Don't worry about us, we will fight as best we can!"
msgstr ""
"Καλή τύχη Κώνραντ! Μην ανυσηχείς για εμάς, θα πολεμήσουμε όσο καλύτερα "
"μπορούμε!"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/01_The_Elves_Besieged.cfg:341
msgid "I... I don't think I can make it anymore."
msgstr "Δε... Δεν νομίζω πως μπορώ να αντέξω άλλο."

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/01_The_Elves_Besieged.cfg:345
msgid "Prince... you must keep fighting! Nooooooo!"
msgstr "Πρίγκιπα... πρέπει να πολεμήσεις! ΌΧΙΙΙΙΙΙΙΙ!"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/01_The_Elves_Besieged.cfg:349
msgid "It is over. I am doomed..."
msgstr "Τελείωσε. Είμαι καταδικασμένος..."

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/01_The_Elves_Besieged.cfg:363
msgid "I have... have failed in my duty to protect the prince! I am defeated."
msgstr "Α...Απότυχα να υπηρετήσω τον πρίγκιπα! Ηττήθηκα."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/01_The_Elves_Besieged.cfg:367
msgid "Don't die, Delfador! Please, you have to stay alive!"
msgstr "Μην πεθάνεις, Ντεφάλντορ! Πρέπει να μείνεις ζωντανός!"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/01_The_Elves_Besieged.cfg:371
#, fuzzy
msgid "Ugh!"
msgstr "ααα"

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/01_The_Elves_Besieged.cfg:382
msgid ""
"Oh, no! We have run out of time, they have arrived with reinforcements..."
msgstr "Ωχ, όχι! Μας τελείωσε ο χρόνος, ήρθαν με ενισχύσεις..."

#. [message]: speaker=second_unit
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/01_The_Elves_Besieged.cfg:401
#, fuzzy
msgid "Die, villain, die!"
msgstr "Πέθανε, κάθαρμα, πέθανε!"

#. [message]: speaker=second_unit
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/01_The_Elves_Besieged.cfg:412
msgid "Only the foolish oppose me!"
msgstr "Μόνο οι ανόητοι μου εναντιώνονται."

#. [message]: speaker=Galdrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/01_The_Elves_Besieged.cfg:423
msgid "I am Galdrad. You will have to fight me to get any further!"
msgstr "Είμαι ο Γκάλραντ, και θα πολεμήσεις εμένα για να προχωρήσεις παραπέρα!"

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/01_The_Elves_Besieged.cfg:434
msgid "Only a fool would dare to attack me!"
msgstr "Μόνο ένας ανόητος θα τολμούσε να μου επιτεθεί!"

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/01_The_Elves_Besieged.cfg:445
msgid "I am Delfador the Great. Prepare to die!"
msgstr "Είμαι ο Ντεφάλντορ ο Μέγας. Ετοιμάσου να πεθάνεις!"

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/01_The_Elves_Besieged.cfg:457
msgid "Let me through, you rogue!"
msgstr "Άφησέ με να περάσω, αλήτη!"

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/01_The_Elves_Besieged.cfg:472
msgid "Oh no! They are destroying our home!"
msgstr "Ωχ, όχι! Πάει το σπίτι μας!"

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/01_The_Elves_Besieged.cfg:476
msgid "There can be no looking back. We must go quickly!"
msgstr "Μην κοιτάς πίσω. Πρέπει να φύγουμε!"

